{
  "verses": [
    {
      "verse_num": 1,
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "narrative",
          "text": "There were present at that season some that told him of the Galilæans, whose blood Pilate had mingled with their sacrifices."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": [],
      "heading": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": 2,
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "narrative",
          "text": "And Jesus answering said unto them,"
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": [],
      "heading": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": 6,
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "narrative",
          "text": "He spake also this parable;"
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": [],
      "heading": [
        "Parable of the Unfruitful Fig Tree"
      ]
    },
    {
      "verse_num": 10,
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "narrative",
          "text": "And he was teaching in one of the synagogues on the sabbath."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": [],
      "heading": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": 11,
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "narrative",
          "text": "And, behold, there was a woman which had a spirit of infirmity eighteen years, and was bowed together, and could in no wise lift up herself."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": [],
      "heading": [
        "Healing of a Crippled Woman"
      ]
    },
    {
      "verse_num": 12,
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "narrative",
          "text": "And when Jesus saw her, he called her to him, and said unto her,"
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": [],
      "heading": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": 13,
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "narrative",
          "text": "And he laid his hands on her: and immediately she was made straight, and glorified God."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": [],
      "heading": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": 14,
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "speech",
          "text": "There are six days in which men ought to work: in them therefore come and be healed, and not on the sabbath day.",
          "speaker": "Ruler of the Synagogue"
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": [],
      "heading": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": 15,
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "narrative",
          "text": "The Lord then answered him, and said,"
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": [],
      "heading": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": 17,
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "narrative",
          "text": "And when he had said these things, all his adversaries were ashamed: and all the people rejoiced for all the glorious things that were done by him."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": [],
      "heading": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": 18,
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "narrative",
          "text": "Then said he,"
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": [],
      "heading": [
        "Parables of Mustard Seed and Leaven"
      ]
    },
    {
      "verse_num": 20,
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "narrative",
          "text": "And again he said,"
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": [],
      "heading": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": 22,
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "narrative",
          "text": "And he went through the cities and villages, teaching, and journeying toward Jerusalem."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": [],
      "heading": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": 23,
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "speech",
          "text": "Lord, are there few that be saved?",
          "speaker": "Unknown"
        },
        {
          "type": "narrative",
          "text": "And he said unto them,"
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": [],
      "heading": [
        "The Narrow Door"
      ]
    },
    {
      "verse_num": 31,
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "speech",
          "text": "Get thee out, and depart hence: for Herod will kill thee.",
          "speaker": "Pharisees"
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": [],
      "heading": [
        "Warning from the Pharisees"
      ]
    },
    {
      "verse_num": 32,
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "narrative",
          "text": "And he said unto them,"
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": [],
      "heading": []
    }
  ]
}